MTGLQ INVESTORS, LP, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Janice M. LAWRENCE, Defendant-Petitioner,
and
Mr. Lawrence, Husband of Janice M. Lawrence and First Financial Federal Credit Union, Defendants. C-517 September Term 2018
081827 Supreme Court of New Jersey. January 25, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-004843-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
